d-price-rises-tipping-point-value-deals-combos-mcdonalds-2024-8%23%3A~%3Atext%3DToo%2520expensive%26amp%3Btext%3DThe%2520cost%2520of%2520labor%2520and%2Crestaurants%2520went%2520up%2520by%25208.2%2525.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoaring%20cost%20of%20labor%20and%20commodities%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%20CEO%20Chris%20Kempczinski%20said%20in%20July%20that%20a%20fall%20in%20sales%20in%20the%20most%20recent%20quarter%20could%20partially%20be%20attributed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-expensive-prices-too-high-fast-food-restaurant-falling-sales-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20food%20being%20too%20expensive%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20consumers%20exploring%20different%20options%20%E2%80%94%20like%20eating%20at%20home%20instead%20%E2%80%94%20restaurants%20have%20realigned%20efforts%20into%20value%20menus.%20Over%20the%20summer%2C%20McDonald's%20and%20Burger%20King%20introduced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburger-king-launches-5-dollar-value-meal-before-mcdonalds-months-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%245%20combo%20deals%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20cheaper%20options%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-mcdonalds-5-dollar-meal-deal-pulling-in-customers-inflation-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappeared%20to%20be%20popular%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bolstering%20visits%20to%20McDonald's%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20restaurant%20business%20is%20facing%20another%20issue.%20Lance%20Zimmerman%2C%20a%20senior%20animal%20protein%20analyst%20for%20Rabo%20AgriFinance%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20beef%20prices%20are%20increasing%20sharply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mcdonalds%20cheeseburger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666345deed9a404d829bc2c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMcDonald's%20has%20suffered%20after%20raising%20prices.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f9ab6d52-d50d-40da-ab5f-be75b38eb654%5C%22%3EThe%20US%20cattle%20herd%20is%20at%20its%20smallest%20in%20seven%20decades%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20beef%20industry%2C%20just%20as%20it%20was%20going%20through%20the%20pandemic%2C%20was%20also%20going%20through%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclimate-fueled-droughts-unearthing-unexpected-discoveries-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworst%20droughts%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%20that%20we%20have%20ever%20had%20in%20the%20last%20100%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20suppliers%20began%20to%20liquidate%20or%20reduce%20the%20cow%20herd.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20beef%20supplies%20are%20getting%20tighter%2C%20meaning%20prices%20are%20increasing%2C%20Zimmerman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20their%20websites%2C%20several%20fast%20food%20chains%20use%20American%20beef%2C%20including%20McDonald's%2C%20Wendy's%2C%20and%20Yum!%20Brands%2C%20which%20owns%20Pizza%20Hut%2C%20Taco%20Bell%2C%20and%20KFC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%20revealed%20that%20the%20US%20cattle%20herd%20fell%20to%2087.2%20million%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%202024%2C%20its%20smallest%20since%201951.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20USDA%20reported%20that%20this%20led%20to%20record%20retail%20beef%20prices%2C%20with%20an%20all-fresh%20value%20of%20%248.15%20per%20pound%20for%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20bad%20news%20for%20hamburger%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20is%20over%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20beef%20prices%20are%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20go%20higher%2C%26quot%3B%20Zimmerman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20problem%20is%20amplified%20by%20beef%20production%20struggling%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20population%20growth.%20Meanwhile%2C%20a%20rise%20in%20US%20exports%20of%20the%20meat%20has%20cut%20domestic%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20issue%20is%20that%20when%20you%20liquidate%20cows%2C%20it%20takes%20about%20two%20years%20to%20replace%20them%2C%20he%20said.%20A%20500-pound%20calf%20has%20to%20first%20more%20than%20double%20in%20size%20before%20breeding%20and%20producing%20its%20own%20calf%2C%20which%20takes%20another%20nine%20months%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Zimmerman%2C%20consumers%20will%20not%20start%20to%20see%20the%20benefits%20of%20stronger%20beef%20supplies%20until%202027%20or%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20don't%20count%20on%20the%20burger%20at%20your%20local%20restaurant%20getting%20any%20cheaper%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e3bdb68-a608-4714-9be4-bc2591bf9ff5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESteak%20prices%20are%20also%20sizzling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20steak%20with%20a%20brown%20crust%20and%20pink%20center%20cooking%20in%20a%20cast-iron%20skillet%20with%20herbed%20butter%20on%20top%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6706ec20a70318649280ad06%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20might%20be%20time%20for%20restaurants%20to%20update%20their%20menus.%3Cp%3EWestend61%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJay%20Bandy%2C%20the%20president%20of%20Goliath%20Consulting%20Group%2C%20a%20Georgia-based%20restaurant%20consulting%20firm%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20beef%20inflation%20is%20a%20problem%20across%20the%20restaurant%20industry%2C%20including%20fine%20dining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20group's%20clients%20has%20had%20to%20raise%20prices%20on%20some%20of%20its%20key%20steak%20items%2C%20and%20another%20is%20considering%20removing%20steak%20and%20fries%20from%20its%20menu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20with%20beef%20prices%20is%20its%20hard%20to%20be%20profitable%20in%20a%20steak-centric%20restaurant%2C%26quot%3B%20Bandy%20said.%20%26quot%3BHigher-end%20dining%20is%20feeling%20more%20of%20a%20pinch%20because%20the%20market%20for%20fine%20dining%20is%20negative%20right%20now.%20It%20peaked%20earlier%20in%20the%20year%2C%20so%20they're%20in%20the%20tough%20spot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20anyone%20wanting%20a%20steak%20should%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeef-expensive-diners-buy-more-steak-at-restaurants-dining-darden-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpect%20to%20pay%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e9592e8b-db8f-4d6b-a079-19f1d2f620f5%5C%22%3ERestaurants%20should%20seize%20this%20opportunity%20to%20find%20beef%20alternatives%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETill%20Dudler%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20global%20consumer%20goods%20and%20services%20strategy%20for%20Accenture%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20strained%20beef%20market%20provides%20real%20opportunities%20for%20restaurants%20to%20update%20their%20menus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20haven't%20seen%20this%20yet%20in%20the%20protein%20space%2C%20but%20in%20the%20ice%20cream%20space%2C%20some%20of%20our%20clients%20will%20basically%20change%20their%20portfolios%20depending%20on%20what%20prices%20are%20out%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20That%20means%20if%20blueberries%20are%20cheap%2C%20expect%20to%20see%20more%20blueberry%20ice%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDudler%20explained%20that%20white%20meat%2C%20like%20chicken%2C%20is%20generally%20a%20good%20substitute.%20He%20also%20said%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20non-meat%20alternatives%2C%20such%20as%20lentils%20and%20chickpeas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChickens%20bred%20for%20meat%20grow%20much%20faster%20than%20cows%20and%20can%20be%20bred%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBandy%20said%20chicken%20is%20one%20of%20the%20main%20alternatives%20he%20has%20been%20advising%20his%20clients%20to%20use%20in%20their%