20to%20ensure%20the%20plan%20works%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20traditional%20definition%20of%20retirement%20is%20when%20you%20quit%20working%20for%20good%20and%20live%20off%20your%20investments%20and%20savings.%20Most%20recently%2C%20though%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Ffinancial-independence-retire-early%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFIRE%20movement%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Financial%20Independence%2C%20Retire%20Early)%20has%20expanded%20this%20definition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20you%20might%20%26quot%3Bretire%26quot%3B%20from%20your%20full-time%20job%20in%20your%2050s%20but%20keep%20a%2010-hour-per-week%20job%20at%20Starbucks%20to%20supplement%20your%20income%20(this%20is%20called%20Barista%20FIRE%2C%20where%20you%20work%20part-time%20into%20retirement).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20aim%20for%20a%20traditional%20retirement%20when%20I%20reach%2045.%20I'm%20open%20to%20the%20possibility%20that%20I%20might%20want%20to%20keep%20running%20my%20own%20business%20by%20then.%20For%20me%2C%20it's%20all%20about%20having%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20do%20these%20three%20things%20consistently%20to%20make%20sure%20I%20stay%20on%20track%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3EI%20use%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmoney-essentials.com%2Forganize-my-finances%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersonal%20financial%20tracker%3C%2Fa%3E%20every%20single%20month%20to%20track%20my%20spending%2C%20income%2C%20and%20investments.%20I%20built%20my%20tracker%20years%20ago%20because%20I%20couldn't%20find%20one%20that%20met%20my%20needs%20online.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20know%20exactly%20how%20much%20I%20need%20to%20save%2C%20spend%2C%20and%20invest%20to%20reach%20my%20goals%2C%20and%20I%20stay%20on%20track%20with%20my%20commitments.%20I%20used%20to%20think%20investing%20so%20much%20would%20feel%20depriving%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20miss%20that%20money.%20I%20fill%20my%20days%20with%20things%20that%20are%20fulfilling%20and%20fr