2C%20run%20data%20centers%20suited%20specifically%20to%20AI%20workloads%20and%20offer%20inference%20services.%20And%20then%20there%20are%20the%20hyperscalers%20like%20AWS%20and%20Microsoft%20Azure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20so%20many%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecompanies%20specializing%20in%20inference%2C%20suspicion%20is%20rising%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20inference%20is%20about%20to%20drop%20off%20a%20cliff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPart%20of%20the%20reason%20inference%20is%20a%20little%20commoditizable%20is%20customers%20are%20kind%20of%20paying%20for%20tokens%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Davis%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20market%20for%20inference%20is%20kind%20of%20like%20the%20electricity%20market%2C%20Davis%20said.%20There%20are%20a%20ton%20of%20niche%20sources%20you%20can%20access%20if%20you%20actually%20shop%20around%2C%20but%20not%20everyone%20does.%20Most%20people%20just%20want%20to%20flip%20the%20light%20switch%20and%20have%20it%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20nuance%20to%20sift%20through%20for%20those%20willing.%20For%20some%20customers%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-competition-sambanova-groq-cerebras-show-faster-inference-speed-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espeed%20is%20of%20the%20utmost%20importance%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Speed%20has%20distinctions%20too%2C%20like%20time%20to%20the%20first%20token%20and%20tokens%20per%20second.%20There's%20total%20job%20completion%20time%20and%20there%20are%20different%20kinds%20of%20inference%20workloads%20that%20lend%20themselves%20to%20different%20computing%20setups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnergy%20efficiency%20of%20the%20underlying%20hardware%20and%20networking%20is%20a%20big%20determinant%20of%20cost.%20And%20cost%20in%20inference%20computing%20is%20even%20more%20important%20than%20in%20training%2C%20Groq%20cofounder%20Jonathan%20Ross%20recently%20told%20BI.%20Training%20is%20an%20overhead%20cost%2C%20while%20inference%20is%20an%20operating%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZoom%20out%20from%20all%20of%20the%20intricacies%2C%20and%20inference%20is%20becoming%20the%20commodity%20of%20the%20AI%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20companies%20just%20want%20output%20and%20they%20don't%20care%20about%20infrastructure%2C%26quot%3B%20Mitesh%20Agrawal%2C%20head%20of%20cloud%20for%20Lambda%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dff58147-0a83-484f-8489-a31c08d0a473%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECommoditizing%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELambda%20is%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20an%20inference-as-a-service%20offering%2C%20but%20Agrawal%20said%20the%20company%20is%20going%20about%20it%20carefully%2C%20focusing%20on%20providing%20holistic%20computing%20services%2C%20and%20not%20just%20tokens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInference%20profit%20margins%20can%20vary%20widely%2C%20Agrawal%20said.%20With%20general%20compute%20%E2%80%94%20where%20the%20customer%20rents%20fixed%20capacity%20%E2%80%94%20the%20margins%20are%20easier%20to%20manage.%20When%20you're%20charging%20for%20usage%20or%20input%20and%20output%20of%20a%20model%2C%20the%20return%20is%20less%20predictable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrganizing%20multiple%20users%20across%20a%20finite%20number%20of%20servers%20takes%20finesse.%20Whether%20or%20not%20the%20cost%20of%20operating%20the%20hardware%20is%20actually%20covered%20with%20room%20for%20profit%20comes%20down%20to%20how%20well%20that%20organization%20is%20done%2C%20Agrawal%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20why%20would%20neoclouds%20offer%20the%20riskier%20service%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgrawal%20said%20it's%20about%20getting%20potential%20customers%20in%20the%20door.%20Inference-as-a-service%20customers%20can%20turn%20into%20more%20traditional%20compute%20customers%2C%20and%20as%20the%20slate%20of%20competitors%20grows%2C%20relationships%2C%20and%20history%20grow%20in%20importance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELambda's%20financial%20models%20assume%20that%20price%20cuts%20are%20coming%20soon%20as%20more%20players%20enter%20the%20inference%20space%20and%20chips%20become%20more%20efficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2259b576b3-4703-4b08-b315-2c7f48e230fb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20race%20to%20the%20bottom%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20fast%20the%20demand%20for%20inference%20is%20growing%20is%20up%20for%20debate%2C%20but%20in%20recent%20public%20statements%2C%20Nvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20has%20said%20on%20multiple%20occasions%20that%20new%20models%2C%20like%20OpenAI's%20o1%2C%20require%20more%20compute%20to%20generate%20the%20same%20number%20of%20responses%20because%20they%20run%20multiple%20models%20to%20check%20their%20own%20work%20or%20%26quot%3Breason.%26quot%3B%20Accuracy%2C%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20requires%20more%20compute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInference%20loads%20are%20poised%20to%20grow%2C%20but%20service%20providers%20still%20anticipate%20a%20drop%20in%20price%20from%20the%20influx%20of%20new%20players.%20Davis%20isn't%20worried%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20recalled%20Jevon's%20paradox%20%E2%80%94%20an%20economic%20principle%20in%20which%20a%20drop%20in%20price%20or%20an%20increase%20in%20efficiency%20leads%20to%20more%20total%20consumption%20%E2%80%94%20like%20when%20you%20widen%20a%20highway%20and%20traffic%20gets%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20make%20something%2010%20times%20cheaper%2C%20people%20won't%20spend%2010%20times%20less%2C%20nor%20will%20they%20even%20hold%20their%20budgets%20the%20same.%20They'll%20spend%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Davis%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20makes%20sense%20because%20what%20are%20you%20doing%20when%20you%20make%20something%2010%20times%20cheaper%2C%20you're%20making%20the%20ROI%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20turns%20out%2C%20when%20you%20make%20inference%20cheaper%2C%20people%20decide%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20more%20inference%2C%26quot%3B%20Davis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ride%20ahead%20could%20be%20%26quot%3Bbumpy%26quot%3B%20though%2C%20and%20not%20all%20players%20are%20likely%20to%20survive%20the%20moments%20of%20mismatch%20between%20supply%20and%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20my%20old%20boss%20at%20Intel%20Andy%20Grove%20used%20to%20say%2C%20'Let%20chaos%20reign%2C%20and%20then%20reign%20in%20the%20chaos'%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sriram%20Viswanathan%2C%20founding%20managing%20partner%20at%20Celesta%20Capital%20and%20investor%20in%20SambaNova%20Systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20agrees%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20next%20few%20years%20will%20be%20wildly%20competitive%20for%20inference%20providers%2C%20but%20he%20believes%20the%20winners%20will%20be%20decided%20on%20merit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20core%20innovation%20can't%20be%20in%20the%20go-to-market%2C%20but%20in%20the%20performance%20and%20power%20of%20the%20underlying%20architecture%2C%26quot%3B%20Viswanathan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20companies%20selling%20tokens%20to%20break%20into%20the%20AI%20market%20aspire%20to%20more.%20The%20chip%20designers%20eventually%20want%20to%20sell%20chips%20to%20hyperscalers%20rather%20than%20inference%20to%20AI%20startups.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20ultimate%20version%20of%20Foundry's%20tech%20is%20bigger%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20do%20our%20job%2C%20right%2C%20you%20know%2C%20we%20will%20be%20a%20core%20part%20of%20how%20every%20GPU%20runs%2C%26quot%3B%20Davis%20said.%20All%20roads%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20run%20through%20inference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHugh%20Langley%20contributed%20reporting.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EGot%20a%20tip%20or%20an%20insight%20to%20share%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cem%3EContact%20Senior%20Reporter%20Emma%20Cosgrove%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aecosgrove%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eecosgrove%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20use%20the%20secure%20messaging%20app%20Signal%3A%20443-333-9088%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2