595.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-2-1728538595-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-2-1728538595-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-2-1728538595-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-2-1728538595-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369599%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKaramveer%E2%80%99s%20dedicated%20preparation%20eventually%20paid%20off%20in%20his%20third%20attempt%20in%202023%2C%20when%20he%20cleared%20the%20UPSC%20exam.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStrategic%20planning%3A%20Key%20to%20Karmveer%E2%80%99s%20UPSC%20success%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20major%20turning%20points%20for%20Karamveer%20was%20his%20realisation%20of%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20CSAT%20exam%20and%20the%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20mastering%20its%20intricacies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20prelims%20comprise%20two%20sections%20of%20General%20Studies%20and%20CSAT.%20The%20latter%20is%20a%20qualifying%20paper%20where%20about%2080%20questions%20are%20asked.%20To%20clear%20the%20exam%2C%20one%20needs%20approximately%2068%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%20200%20marks.%20In%20my%20first%20attempt%2C%20although%20I%20scored%20well%20in%20General%20Studies%2C%20I%20failed%20in%20CSAT%20by%20just%20three%20marks.%20To%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20the%20gap%20increased%20to%20nine%20marks%20when%20I%20reappeared%20for%20the%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20a%20middle-income%20background%2C%20Karamveer%20also%20faced%20immense%20pressure%20at%20home.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20and%20our%20family%20was%20surviving%20on%20his%20monthly%20pension.%20There%20is%20immense%20uncertainty%20in%20this%20exam%2C%20and%20having%20failed%20twice%20added%20to%20the%20pressure.%20My%20family%20was%20confused%20about%20why%20I%20could%20not%20even%20clear%20the%20prelims.%20It%20was%20becoming%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20stay%20motivated%20given%20the%20circumstances%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-1-1728538558.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Karamveer%20suggests%20analysing%20the%20last%2010%20years%E2%80%99%20question%20papers%20and%20their%20answer%20keys%20to%20improve%20marks%20in%20CSAT.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-1-1728538558.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-1-1728538558-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-1-1728538558-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-1-1728538558-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-1-1728538558-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369597%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKaramveer%20suggests%20analysing%20the%20last%2010%20years%E2%80%99%20question%20papers%20and%20their%20answer%20keys%20to%20improve%20marks%20in%20CSAT.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CSAT%20section%20continued%20to%20haunt%20him.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20genuinely%20scared%20of%20CSAT.%20I%20needed%20to%20improve%20my%20strategy%20for%20this%20section%2C%20as%20I%20was%20performing%20well%20in%20General%20Studies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20his%20mistakes%2C%20Karamveer%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CComing%20from%20an%20engineering%20background%2C%20I%20was%20overly%20confident%20that%20I%20would%20be%20able%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360088%2Fupsc-cse-hindi-medium-aspirants-ifs-officer-vikas-singh-meena-shares-tips-study-material-current-affairs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20clear%20CSAT%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20focussing%20solely%20on%20Maths%20and%20Logical%20Reasoning.%20I%20neglected%20the%20English%20comprehension%20section%20and%20even%20avoided%20questions%20that%20seemed%20doable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20an%20aspirant%2C%20we%20should%20not%20forget%20that%20UPSC%20tests%20your%20abilities%20in%20every%20section.%20You%20cannot%20choose%20to%20opt-out%20of%20topics%20that%20you%20are%20not%20comfortable%20with.%20In%20my%20third%20attempt%2C%20I%20set%20my%20ego%20aside%20and%20gave%20equal%20weight%20to%20all%20three%20sections.%20That%20is%20what%20UPSC%20expects%20%E2%80%94%20do%20not%20neglect%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20overcome%20the%20challenges%20presented%20by%20this%20crucial%20component%20of%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F362685%2Fhow-to-clear-upsc-cse-from-home-irms-officer-akash-chavda-prep-journey-delhi-coaching-busting-myths%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20UPSC%20examination%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Karamveer%20strategically%20adjusted%20his%20preparation%20approach.%20He%20dedicated%20about%20three%20hours%20of%20study%20each%20day%20for%20three%20months%20to%20excel%20in%20this%20section.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20merely%20attempting%20more%20comprehension%20questions%20was%20not%20enough.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20times%2C%20questions%20on%20basics%20like%20permutations%20and%20combinations%2C%20profit%20and%20loss%2C%20and%20percentages%20are%20designed%20to%20challenge%20even%20IIT%20students.%20To%20ace%20both%20Maths%20and%20Logical%20Reasoning%2C%20I%20started%20referring%20to%20notes%20meant%20for%20the%20CAT%20(Common%20Admission%20Test)%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaramveer%20also%20began%20analysing%20the%20last%2010%20years%E2%80%99%20question%20papers%20and%20their%20answer%20keys.%20This%20analysis%20helped%20him%20understand%20the%20type%20of%20questions%20to%20expect%20in%20the%20exam.%20By%20focusing%20on%20all%20three%20sections%20of%20the%20CSAT%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20questions%20he%20attempted.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20he%20says%2C%20he%20could%20score%2090%20out%20of%20the%20200%20marks%20in%20the%20exam%20on%20his%20third%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaramveer%20highlights%20the%20significance%20of%20perseverance%2C%20adaptability%2C%20and%20strategic%20planning%20in%20overcoming%20challenges%20and%20achieving%20one%E2%80%99s%20goals.%20His%20journey%20underscores%20the%20importance%20of%20a%20well-rounded%20preparation%20strategy%20that%20encompasses%20not%20only%20a%20strong%20grasp%20of%20the%20subject%20matter%20but%20also%20a%20keen%20understanding%20of%20the%20exam%E2%80%99s%20specific%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee.%20All%20photos%3A%20Karamveer%20Narwaniya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728892315000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcsat-2-1728538595.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D369549%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20performing%20well%20in%20the%20General%20Studies%20paper%2C%20Karamveer%20Narwaniya%20failed%20in%20the%20CSAT%20section%2C%20a%20critical%20part%20of%20the%20UPSC%20Civil%20Services%20Exam.%20Here's%20how%20he%20changed%20his%20strategy%20to%20master%20the%20intricacies%20to%20clear%20the%20qualifying%20exam.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%2