post%20on%20LinkedIn%3C%2Fa%3E%20paid%20a%20beautiful%20tribute%20to%20his%20mentor%2C%20reminiscing%20about%20the%20time%20he%20spent%20with%20him.%20Mr%20Chandrasekaran%20reflected%20on%20the%20legendary%20industrialist's%20profound%20impact%2C%20noting%20that%20everyone%20who%20met%20him%20came%20away%20with%20a%20story%20about%20his%20kindness%2C%20warmth%2C%20and%20vision%20for%20India.%20He%20also%20remarked%20how%20Mr%20Tata's%C2%A0remarkable%20ability%20to%20connect%20with%20people%20and%20notice%20details%20made%20him%20truly%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Our%20relationship%20grew%20over%20the%20years%2C%20first%20focusing%20on%20business%20and%20eventually%20evolving%20into%20a%20more%20personal%20connection.%20We%20discussed%20interests%20ranging%20from%20cars%20to%20hotels%2C%20but%20when%20our%20conversations%20turned%20to%20other%20matters%E2%80%94those%20of%20daily%20life%E2%80%94he%20would%20show%20how%20much%20he%20noticed%20and%20felt.%20He%20was%20someone%20to%20be%20discovered%2C%20over%20time%20and%20through%20experience%2C''%20he%20wrote%20in%20a%20LinkedIn%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chandrasekaran%20fondly%20recalled%20a%20pivotal%20moment%20in%202017%20when%20he%20and%20Ratan%20Tata%20collaborated%20to%20resolve%20a%20longstanding%20wage%20dispute%20between%20Tata%20Motors%20and%20its%20employees'%20union.%20In%20a%20meeting%20with%20union%20leaders%2C%20Mr%20Tata%20expressed%20regret%20over%20the%20delay%2C%20candidly%20discussed%20the%20company's%20challenges%2C%20and%20assured%20a%20prompt%20resolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Mr.%20Tata's%20direction%20squarely%20focused%20on%20making%20sure%20employees%20were%20well%20taken%20care%20of%E2%80%94not%20just%20to%20resolve%20the%20dispute%2C%20but%20to%20ensure%20their%20and%20their%20families'%20well-being.%20Across%20other%20Group%20companies%2C%20his%20perspective%20on%20employees%20was%20uniform.%20It%20is%20something%20that%20has%20shaped%20a%20number%20of%20our%20leaders%20across%20the%20Group%2C''%20the%20Chairman%20noted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EN.%20Chandrasekaran%20shared%20another%C2%A0fascinating%20story%20about%20the%20renovation%20of%20Bombay%20House%2C%20Tata%20Group's%20iconic%20headquarters.%20The%20heritage%20building%2C%20constructed%20in%201924%2C%20had%20remained%20untouched%20for%20decades%2C%20earning%20it%20the%20reputation%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btemple%26quot%3B%20that%20shouldn't%20be%20altered.%20When%C2%A0%20N.%20Chandrasekaran%20discussed%C2%A0renovating%20Bombay%20House%20with%20Ratan%20Tata%2C%20his%20initial%20concern%C2%A0was%20about%20the%20well-being%20of%20dogs.%20''May%20I%20ask%20you%20something%3F%20When%20you%20say%20%E2%80%98renovate'%2C%20do%20you%20mean%20%E2%80%98vacate'%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20explained%20that%20we%20planned%20to%20move%20everyone%20to%20a%20nearby%20office.%20He%20gently%20clarified%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhere%20will%20the%20dogs%20go%3F''%2C%20the%20post%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chandrasekaran%20reassured%20Mr%20Tata%20that%20a%20kennel%20would%20be%20built%20to%20care%20for%20the%20dogs%2C%20bringing%20a%20smile%20to%20his%20face.%20Upon%20completion%20of%20the%20renovation%2C%20Mr%20Tata's%20first%20request%20was%20to%20see%20the%20kennel%2C%20demonstrating%20his%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20compassion%20and%20detail.%20''Seeing%20his%20happiness%20with%20the%20kennel%20and%20his%20priorities%20was%20a%20reminder%20that%20while%20big%20projects%20are%20important%2C%20it's%20the%20details%20that%20reveal%20how%20we%20think%2C%20what%20we%20prioritise%2C%20and%20how%20we%20are%20perceived.%20His%20joy%20was%20confirmation%20that%20we%20had%20done%20the%20right%20thing%2C''%20Mr%20Chandrasekaran%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20highlighted%20Ratan%20Tata's%20exceptional%20memory%20and%20meticulous%20attention%20to%20detail%2C%20showcasing%20his%20remarkable%20leadership%20qualities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Mr.%20Tata%20ever%20visited%20a%20place%2C%20he%20could%20recall%20everything%E2%80%94from%20the%20placement%20of%20smallest%20piece%20of%20furniture%2C%20the%20lighting%2C%20colours%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20His%20memory%20was%20photographic.%20He%20remembered%20the%20covers%20and%20content%20of%20books%20and%20magazines%20and%20referred%20to%20them%20even%20years%20later.%20He%20was%20always%20observing%20and%20processing%2C%20from%20large%20ideas%20to%20minute%20detail%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chandrasekaran%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20concluded%20his%20tribute%20post%2C%20saying%2C%20''There%20is%20so%20much%20else%20to%20say%20about%20who%20he%20was%2C%20but%20for%20now%2C%20as%20I%20process%20his%20absence%2C%20this%20will%20have%20to%20do%3A%20His%20eye%20received%20everything%20clearly%2C%20as%20his%20mind%20perceived%20everything%20clearly.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERatan%20Tata%20died%20on%20October%209%20at%20Mumbai's%20Breach%20Candy%20Hospital%2C%20where%20he%20was%20admitted%20for%20a%20routine%20health%20check%20due%20to%20his%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728887160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fj9dmtmh_n-chandrasekaran-with-ratan-tata-_625x300_14_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fno-one-like-him-tata-sons-chairman-n-chandrasekaran-shares-untold-stories-of-ratan-tata-6784745%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mr%20Chandrasekaran%20reflected%20on%20the%20legendary%20industrialist's%20profound%20impact%2C%20noting%20that%20everyone%20who%20met%20him%20came%20away%20with%20a%20story%20about%20his%20kindness%2C%20warmth%2C%20and%20vision%20for%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fno-one-like-him-tata-sons-chairman-n-chandrasekaran-shares-untold-stories-of-ratan-tata-6784745%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bone%20Test%20Rules%20Out%20Baba%20Siddique%20Shooter's%20Claim%20Of%20Being%20Minor%3A%2010%20Po