C%20Women's%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20Indian%20skipper%20Harmanpreet%20Kaur%20said%20that%20she%20and%20Deepti%20Sharma%20failed%20to%20punish%20a%20few%20balls%20from%20their%20opponents%20during%20their%20partnership%2C%20which%20ultimately%20contributed%20to%20their%20loss.%20A%20brilliant%20final%20over%20by%20Annabel%20Sutherland%20helped%20Australia%20survive%20a%20scare%20from%20Indian%20skipper%20Harmanpreet%20Kaur%20as%20the%20Women%20in%20Blue%20fell%20just%20nine%20runs%20short%20in%20their%20run%20chase%20of%20152%20runs%20in%20their%20ICC%20Women's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20match%20at%20Sharjah%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20game%2C%20Harmanpreet%20said%20in%20the%20post-match%20presentation%20that%20the%20key%20difference%20between%20both%20sides%20was%20the%20Australian%20team%20not%20depending%20on%20just%20one%20or%20two%20players%20and%20having%20some%20fine%20all-rounders%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20their%20entire%20team%20contribute%2C%20they%20don't%20depend%20on%20one%20or%20two%20players%2C%20they%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20all-rounders%20who%20contribute.%20We%20also%20planned%20well%20and%20we%20were%20there%20in%20the%20game.%20They%20didn't%20give%20away%20easy%20runs%20and%20made%20it%20difficult.%20They%20are%20an%20experienced%20side.%20That%20is%20something%20that%20is%20not%20in%20your%20control%2C%20you%20have%20to%20always%20keep%20your%20playing%20eleven%20ready%20even%20when%20one%20or%20two%20player%20misses%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Harmanpreet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRadha%20bowled%20really%20well%2C%20she%20was%20in%20the%20game%20and%20she%20was%20fielding%20well.%20You%20need%20a%20character%20like%20that%20in%20the%20team%20who%20is%20always%20there.%20It%20was%20a%20chaseable%20total.%20When%20me%20and%20Deepti%20were%20batting%2C%20we%20could%20not%20hit%20a%20few%20loose%20balls.%20We%20can%20learn%20a%20lot%20from%20Australia.%20Whatever%20was%20in%20our%20hands%2C%20we%20were%20trying%20to%20do%20that%20but%20that%20is%20something%20not%20in%20our%20control.%20If%20we%20get%20the%20opportunity%20to%20play%20another%20game%2C%20that%20will%20be%20great.%20But%20otherwise%2C%20whoever%20deserves%20to%20be%20there%2C%20that%20team%20will%20be%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20Australia%20opted%20to%20bat%20first%20after%20winning%20the%20toss.%20Knocks%20from%20Grace%20Harris%20(40%20in%2041%20balls%2C%20with%20five%20fours)%20and%20Tahlia%20McGrath%20(32%20in%2026%20balls%2C%20with%20four%20boundaries)%20helped%20them%20reach%20151%2F8%2C%20despite%20a%20fine%20comeback%20by%20Indian%20spinners%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERenuka%20Singh%20(2%2F24)%20and%20Deepti%20Sharma%20(2%2F28)%20were%20the%20top%20bowlers%20for%20India.%20Shreyanka%20Patil%2C%20Pooja%20Vastrakar%20and%20Radha%20Yadav%20also%20got%20a%20wicket%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20run-chase%20of%20152%20runs%2C%20India%20lost%20some%20early%20wickets%2C%20but%20a%20partnership%20between%20Deepti%20Sharma%20(29%20in%2025%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours)%20and%20skipper%20Harmanpreet%20(54*%20in%2047%20balls%2C%20with%20six%20fours)%20took%20India%20to%20touching%20distance%20of%20a%20win.%20India%20needed%2014%20runs%20in%20the%20final%20over%2C%20but%20Annabel%20Sutherland%20left%20India%20nine%20runs%20short%20of%20the%20winning%20total%20with%20her%20consistent%20bowling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia%20moves%20into%20the%20semifinals%20with%20four%20wins%20in%20four%20games.%20While%20India%20placed%20at%20second%20spot%20with%20two%20wins%20and%20two%20losses%2C%20will%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20result%20of%20New%20Zealand%20versus%20Pakistan%20match%20to%20confirm%20their%20fate%20and%20will%20have%20to%20root%20for%20their%20arch-rivals%2C%20who%20sit%20at%20two%20points%20to%20have%20net%20run-rate%20come%20into%20the%20equation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESutherland%20(2%2F22)%20and%20Molineux%20(2%2F32)%20were%20the%20top%20bowlers%20for%20Australia.%20Schutt%20and%20Gardner%20got%20one%20wicket%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728882840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F1e1mr7lg_harmanpreet-kaur-x_625x300_14_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwomen-s-t20-world-cup%2Faustralia-dont-depend-on-one-or-two-players-harmanpreet-kaurs-fiery-take-on-indias-defeat-6782416%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Following%20the%20game%2C%20Harmanpreet%20said%20in%20the%20post-match%20presentation%20that%20the%20key%20difference%20between%20both%20sides%20was%20the%20Australian%20team%20not%20depending%20on%20just%20one%20or%20two%20players%20and%20having%20some%20fine%20all-rounders%20too.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwomen-s-t20-world-cup%2Faustralia-dont-depend-on-one-or-two-players-harmanpreet-kaurs-fiery-take-on-indias-defeat-6782416%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-Eng%20captain%20slams%20Pakistan%20for%20dropping%20Babar%20Azam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728882658000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114204686%2Cimgsize-53030.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fstupid-decision-former-england-captain-michael-vaughan-slams-pakistan-for-dropping-babar-azam%2Farticleshow%2F114204676.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Babar%20Azam%20was%20dropped%20for%20Pakistan's%20second%20Test%20against%20England%20following%20an%20innings%20defeat%20in%20the%20first%20Test.%20Former%20England%20captain%20Michael%20Vaughan%20criticized%20the%20decision.%20Other%20key%20players%2C%20including%20Shaheen%20Afridi%2C%20Naseem%20Shah%2C%20and%20Sarfaraz%20Ahmed%2C%20were%20also%20dropped%20to%20help%20them%20regain%20form%20and%20confidence.%20Babar%2C%20who%20recently%20stepped%20down%20as%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20white-ball%20captain%2C%20has%20faced%20criticism%20for%20his%20underwhelming%20form%20with%20the%20bat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fstupid-decision-former-england-captain-michael-vaughan-slams-pakistan-for-dropping-babar-azam%2Farticleshow%2F114204676.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Key%20Doctors'%20Body%20Pauses%20Strike%20As%20Bengal%20Calls%20Meet%20To%20Discuss%20Demands%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Federation%20of%20All%20India%20Medical%20Association%20(FAIMA)%2C%20the%20key%20doctors'%20body%2C%20today%20paused%20its%20nationwide%20shutdown%20of%20elective%20services%20in%20hospitals%20in%20solidarity%20with%20medics'%20ongoing%20protest%20in%20West%20Bengal%20after%20the%20state%20government%20called%20a%20meeting%20to%20discuss%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20closely%20assess%20this%20meeting's%20outcome%20to%20ensure%20it%20meets%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Junior%20Doctors'%20Front%20(WBJDF).%20If%20the%20meeting%20fails%20to%20produce%20satisfactory%20results%2C%20we%20will%20proceed%20with%20a%20complete%20boycott%20from%20October%2015%20onward%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20FAIMA%20said%2C%20which%20yesterday%20had%20called%20for%20a%20nationwide%20strike%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEmergency%20services%20will%20remain%20unaffected%20to%20uphold%20our%20commitment%20to%20urgent%20patient%20care%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20Chief%20Secretary%20Manoj%20Pant%20has%20invited%20representatives%20of%20key%20doctors'%20bodies%20for%20a%20meeting%20on%20Monday%20at%20the%20state%20health%20department%20headquarters%20Swasthya%20Bhawan%20to%20discuss%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%2C%20Mr%20Pant%20also%20urged%20the%20Joint%20Platform%20of%20Doctors%20(JPD)%20to%20%26quot%3Badvise%26quot%3B%20the%20junior%20doctors%20to%20end%20their%20hunger%20strike%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20their%20health%20and%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-rg-kar-medical-college-rape-kolkata-rape-no-assurance-key-doctors-body-says-strike-over-kolkata-rape-to-continue-6330403%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJunior%20doctors%20in%20West%20Bengal%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20on%20fast-unto-death%20since%20October%205%20demanding%20justice%20for%20the%2031-year-old%20woman%20medic%2C%20who%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frg-kar-rape-and-murder-over-200-senior-doctors-resign-in-support-of-juniors-protest-in-bengal-6754758%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Kolkata%20on%20August%209.%20Their%20fast%20followed%20nearly%2050%20days%20of%20'cease%20work'%20in%20two%20phases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20other%20demands%20include%20establishing%20a%20centralised%20referral%20system%20for%20all%20hospitals%20and%20medical%20colleges%20in%20the%20state%2C%20implementing%20a%20bed%20vacancy%20monitoring%20system%2C%20and%20forming%20task%20forces%20to%20ensure%20essential%20provisions%20for%20CCTV%2C%20on-call%20rooms%2C%20and%20washrooms%20at%20their%20workplaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20doctors%20have%20so%20far%20been%20hospitalised%20after%20their%20health%20condition%20deteriorated%20due%20to%20fasting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20exhaustive%20discussions%2C%20we%20have%20unanimously%20decided%20that%20it%20is%20time%20to%20unite%20on%20a%20national%20scale.%20We%20had%20given%20an%20ultimatum%20for%20escalation%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20West%20Bengal%20in%20a%20previous%20letter%2C%20however%20no%20satisfactory%20action%20has%20been%20seen%2C%20compelling%20us%20to%20request%20all%20RDAs%20(Resident%20Doctors'%20Associations)%20and%20medical%20associations%20across%20the%20country%20to%20join%20us%20in%20our%20call%20for%20a%20shutdown%20of%20elective%20services%20across%20the%20country%2C%20commencing%20Monday%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20FAIMA%20had%20said%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20decision%20we%20have%20taken%20lightly.%20We%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20implications%20this%20has%20for%20the%20general%20public%2C%20and%20it%20pains%20us%20to%20consider%20any%20action%20that%20might%20cause%20them%20distress.%20But%20our%20voices%20have%20been%20ignored%2C%20our%20safety%20compromised%2C%20and%20our%20appeals%20dismissed%20by%20the%20government%20for%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20addressed%20to%20National%20Medical%20Associations%2C%20state%20Resident%20Doctors'%20Associations%20(RDAs)%20and%20Resident%20Doctors'%20Associations%20(RDAs)%20from%20various%20medical%20colleges%20and%20institutes%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20afford%20to%20lose%20another%20colleague%20to%20violence%20or%20neglect.%20The%20apathy%20of%20the%20government%20has%20left%20us%20with%20no%20other%20choice.%20It%20is%20with%20a%20heavy%20heart%20but%20steadfast%20determination%20that%20we%20ask%20all%20RDAs%20to%20convene%20immediate%20general%20body%20meetings%20and%20urge%20you%20to%20join%20us%20in%20solidarity%20with%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Junior%20Doctors'%20Front%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728882300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fs4gmlob_doctors-protests_625x300_14_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkey-doctors-body-faima-pauses-strike-as-bengal-calls-meet-to-discuss-demands-after-rg-kar-hospital-doctor-ra