0also%20killed%20nearly%202%2C500%20people%20and%20injured%2010%2C000%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20does%20THAAD%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETHAAD%20is%20designed%20to%20intercept%20incoming%20ballistic%20missiles%20during%20the%20%26quot%3Bterminal%20phase%26quot%3B%20of%20their%20flight%20-%20the%20final%20stage%20before%20impact.%20This%20system%20can%20target%20missiles%20both%20inside%20and%20outside%20the%20atmosphere%20(endoatmospheric%20and%20exoatmospheric).%20THAAD%20defends%20against%20short%2C%20medium%20and%20intermediate-range%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20making%20it%20highly%20adaptable%20to%20various%20types%20of%20missile%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20unique%20feature%20of%20the%20system%20is%20that%20it%20does%20not%20carry%20explosive%20warheads.%20Instead%2C%20it%20destroys%20targets%20using%20kinetic%20energy%2C%20meaning%20it%20hits%20incoming%20missiles%20with%20force%20rather%20than%20detonating%20a%20warhead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EComponents%20of%20THAAD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETHAAD%20is%20composed%20of%20four%20main%20elements%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInterceptor%3A%20Destroys%20incoming%20missiles%20using%20impact%20force.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELaunch%20vehicle%3A%20Mobile%20trucks%20that%20carry%20and%20launch%20the%20interceptors.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERadar%3A%20Tracks%20and%20detects%20threats%20from%20a%20range%20of%20870%20to%203%2C000%20km.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFire%20control%20system%3A%20Coordinates%20the%20launching%20and%20targeting%20of%20interceptors.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20standard%20THAAD%20battery%20includes%20six%20truck-mounted%20launchers%2C%20each%20carrying%20up%20to%20eight%20interceptors%2C%20along%20with%20radar%20and%20radio%20equipment.%20Reloading%20each%20launcher%20takes%20about%2030%20minutes%2C%20and%20a%20full%20battery%20requires%2095%20US%20soldiers%20to%20operate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS%20role%20in%20THAAD%20deployment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20critical%20aspects%20of%20THAAD%20is%20that%20it%20is%20exclusively%20operated%20by%20US%20personnel.%20If%20deployed%20in%20Israel%2C%20this%20would%20require%20the%20presence%20of%20US%20troops%20on%20Israeli%20soil.%20The%20US%20Army%20currently%20possesses%20seven%20THAAD%20batteries%20deployed%20in%20various%20global%20conflict%20zones%20as%20part%20of%20its%20defensive%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20send%20THAAD%20to%20Israel%20made%20just%20weeks%20before%20the%20US%20presidential%20election%2C%20marks%20the%20first%20major%20US%20military%20deployment%20to%20Israel%20since%20the%20country%20started%20bombing%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728880800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F8hngd92o_thaad-reuters-_625x300_14_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthaad-explained-the-advanced-missile-defense-system-the-us-is-deploying-to-israel-6784124%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20United%20States%20has%20deployed%20one%20of%20its%20most%20advanced%20missile%20defence%20systems%2C%20the%20Terminal%20High%20Altitude%20Area%20Defense%20(THAAD)%2C%20along%20with%20100%20US%20troops%20to%20Israel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthaad-explained-the-advanced-missile-defense-system-the-us-is-deploying-to-israel-6784124%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20calls%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20'brilliant%2C'%20says%20US%20faces%20greater%20threats%20from%20'enemies%20within'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728880569000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114203122%2Cimgsize-930744.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-calls-chinese-president