%20whole%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20fighting%20raged%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hezbollah%20forces%20in%20Lebanon's%20south%2C%20United%20Nations%20peacekeepers%20said%20they%20had%20again%20in%20the%20firing%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20Israeli%20troops%20%26quot%3Bforcibly%26quot%3B%20entered%20a%20UN%20position%20with%20two%20tanks%2C%20after%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20called%20on%20the%20force%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20said%20a%20tank%20had%20backed%20into%20the%20UN%20post%20while%20under%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHezbollah%20promises%20worse%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran-backed%20Hezbollah%20said%20late%20Sunday%20that%20it%20launched%20%26quot%3Ba%20squadron%20of%20attack%20drones%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20Binyamina%20camp%2C%20around%2030%20kilometres%20(20%20miles)%20south%20of%20the%20major%20city%20of%20Haifa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20was%20in%20response%20to%20Israeli%20attacks%2C%20including%20air%20strikes%20on%20Thursday%20that%20Lebanon's%20health%20ministry%20said%20killed%20at%20least%2022%20people%20in%20central%20Beirut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20later%20statement%2C%20Hezbollah%20warned%20Israel%20that%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20it%20witnessed%20today%20in%20southern%20Haifa%20is%20nothing%20compared%20to%20what%20awaits%20it%20if%20it%20decides%20to%20continue%20its%20aggression%20against%20our%20noble%20and%20dear%20people%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Israeli%20volunteer%20rescue%20service%2C%20United%20Hatzalah%2C%20said%20its%20teams%20in%20Binyamina%20assisted%20%26quot%3Bover%2060%20wounded%20people%26quot%3B%20with%20injuries%20from%20mild%20to%20critical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20has%20been%20firing%20rockets%20and%20drones%20into%20Israel%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year%20in%20support%20of%20Hamas%20militants%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20late%20September%2C%20however%2C%20its%20strikes%20have%20reached%20further%20into%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20sophisticated%20air%20defences%20have%20intercepted%20most%20of%20the%20projectiles%2C%20with%20few%20casualties%20caused%20by%20strikes%20or%20falling%20debris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDefend%20this%20'blessed%20land'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20recent%20strikes%20have%20increasingly%20focused%20on%20areas%20beyond%20Hezbollah's%20traditional%20strongholds%20in%20southern%20Beirut%2C%20and%20Lebanon's%20south%20and%20east.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20said%20its%20air%20force%20hit%20%26quot%3BHezbollah%20launchers%2C%20anti-tank%20missile%20posts%2C%20weapons%20storage%20facilities%26quot%3B%20and%20other%20targets%2C%20while%20on%20the%20ground%20its%20soldiers%20%26quot%3Beliminated%20dozens%26quot%3B%20of%20fighters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELebanon's%20official%20National%20News%20Agency%20(NNA)%20said%20Israeli%20forces%20had%20%26quot%3Bescalated%20their%20attacks%26quot%3B%20on%20southern%20Lebanon%20with%20%26quot%3Bsuccessive%20air%20strikes%26quot%3B%20pounding%20several%20border%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20later%20reported%20that%20an%20Israeli%20strike%20on%20Mayfadoun%2C%20near%20Nabatiyeh%2C%20in%20southern%20Lebanon%2C%20had%20killed%20five%20people%20and%20wounded%20one%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20said%20its%20forces%20clashed%20several%20times%20with%20Israeli%20troops%20who%20tried%20to%20%26quot%3Binfiltrate%26quot%3B%20villages%20along%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20drone%20strike%20it%20had%20said%20it%20launched%20a%20salvo%20of%20rockets%20at%20a%20%26quot%3Bbase%20in%20southern%20Haifa%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20later%20aired%20an%20audio%20recording%20of%20its%20slain%20leader%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20calling%20on%20fighters%20to%20%26quot%3Bdefend%20this%20holy%20and%20blessed%20land%20and%20this%20honourable%20people%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENasrallah%20was%20killed%20in%20an%20Israeli%20air%20strike%20in%20south%20Beirut%20on%20September%2027%2C%20and%20several%20other%20senior%20commanders%20of%20the%20movement%20have%20also%20been%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20said%20about%20115%20projectiles%20fired%20by%20Hezbollah%20had%20crossed%20into%20Israeli%20territory%20by%20Sunday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Hezbollah%20fighter%20was%20captured%20emerging%20from%20a%20tunnel%20in%20south%20Lebanon%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Israel's%20military%20said%2C%20the%20first%20such%20announcement%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20ground%20offensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Shocking%20violations'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUN%20peacekeepers%20accused%20Israeli%20troops%20of%20breaking%20through%20a%20gate%20and%20entering%20one%20of%20their%20positions%20before%20dawn%20Sunday%20in%20south%20Lebanon%2C%20the%20latest%20of%20several%20incidents%20the%20UNIFIL%20mission%20has%20reported%20since%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20Blue%20Helmets%20have%20so%20far%20been%20injured%2C%20provoking%20international%20condemnation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo%20IDF%20(Israeli%20military)%20Merkava%20tanks%20destroyed%20the%20position's%20main%20gate%20and%20forcibly%20entered%20the%20position%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Ramia%20area%2C%20before%20leaving%2045%20minutes%20later%2C%20UNIFIL%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20later%20said%20a%20tank%20%26quot%3Bbacked%20several%20meters%20into%20a%20UNIFIL%20post%26quot%3B%20while%20%26quot%3Bunder%20fire%26quot%3B%20and%20attempting%20to%20evacuate%20injured%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20Sunday%2C%20Netanyahu%20had%20called%20on%20the%20UN%20to%20move%20peacekeepers%20in%20southern%20Lebanon%20out%20of%20harm's%20way%2C%20after%20the%20mission%20rejected%20requests%20to%20abandon%20its%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20peacekeepers'%20presence%20had%20%26quot%3Bthe%20effect%20of%20providing%20Hezbollah%20terrorists%20wi