es%20are%20smaller.%20You%20can%20only%20fit%20so%20much%20stuff%20in%20these%20little%20houses%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20want%20it%20to%20be%20overrun%20with%20stuff%20you%20buy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22818826b7-02f9-4177-b3a7-5b544fda946c%5C%22%3ELess%20choice%2C%20more%20freedom%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20says%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-and-worst-things-about-living-in-scotland-uk-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elife%20in%20Scotland%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20simpler%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20exactly%20what%20they%20were%20looking%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20in%20the%20US%2C%20where%20a%20lot%20of%20stores%20are%20open%2024%2F7%2C%20stores%20in%20their%20area%20tend%20to%20close%20early%20on%20Fridays%20or%20not%20open%20at%20all%20on%20Sundays%2C%20Zach%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20helped%20them%20rethink%20their%20consumption%20habits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20kind%20of%20forced%20into%20this%20slower%20rhythm%2C%20where%20it's%20like%20'OK%2C%20I%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20this%20thing%20now%2C'%26quot%3B%20Zach%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20I%20have%20to%20wait%20a%20few%20days%20for%20it%2C%20then%20it's%20not%20that%20urgent%2C%20and%20maybe%20I%20never%20needed%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20lot%20like%20the%20old%20days%2C%20he%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BBack%20when%20we%20were%20growing%20up%2C%20you%20didn't%20just%20have%20things%20turning%20up%20in%20your%20door%20the%20next%20day.%20You'd%20have%20to%20get%20a%20catalog%20through%20the%20mail%20and%20sign%20away%20for%20it%2C%20and%20then%20two%20weeks%20later%2C%20maybe%20it%20would%20turn%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20in%20a%20smaller%20town%20like%20theirs%2C%20there's%20less%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-too-much-choice-is-bad-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edecision%20fatigue%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20not%20as%20much%20choice%20at%20the%20grocery%20stores.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20salad%20dressing%2C%20you%20have%20an%20entire%20aisle%20of%20dressing%20and%20then%20around%20the%20corner%2C%20in%20the%20refrigerated%20section%2C%20there's%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Annie%20said.%20%26quot%3BOver%20here%2C%20we%20went%20to%20our%20local%20shop%2C%20and%20there%20were%20three%20to%20choose%20from.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20the%20couple%20realized%20that%20it's%20quite%20common%20for%20people%20to%20make%20things%20from%20scratch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20trying%20to%20reframe%20our%20mentality%2C%20and%20we%20have%20a%20bit%20more%20time%20now%2C%20so%20it's%20like%2C%20why%20don't%20I%20enjoy%20the%20process%20and%20maybe%20make%20my%20own%20dressing%20too%3F%26quot%3B%20Annie%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246f873d6-b62e-4f1f-8343-5dc47c893d20%5C%22%3ESlowing%20down%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22869%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20little%20girl%20sitting%20on%20an%20adult's%20shoulders.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66da51f85444ffafa762fcea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22652%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20says%20they%20spend%20more%20time%20outdoors%20as%20a%20family.%3Cp%3EZach%20and%20Annie%2FSimple%20Scottish%20Living%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELife%20in%20Scotland%20is%20slower%20compared%20to%20California%2C%20in%20part%20due%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-work-life-balance-work-psychologists-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebetter%20work-life%20balance%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20normal%20for%20some%20businesses%20to%20take%20longer%20lunch%20breaks%20and%20turn%20off%20their%20phones%20for%20an%20hour%20or%20two%20during%20the%20day%2C%20Zach%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20hard%20to%20reach%20people%20after%20work%20hours%2C%