%2C%20scorpions%2C%20and%20snakes%20interpret%20the%20absence%20of%20doors%20as%20an%20invitation%20to%20flit%20in%20and%20out%20as%20they%20please%3B%20meaning%20sleepless%20nights%20for%20the%20shanty%E2%80%99s%20residents%20%E2%80%94%20women%20of%20the%20Madia%20community%20who%20are%20exiled%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekurma%20ghar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(period%20hut)%20during%20%3Cem%3Epali%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F267937%2Fmenstrual-health-period-poverty-delhi-pinkishe-social-impact-facebook-community%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emenstrual%20cycle%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20inhumanity%20spotlights%20the%20degree%20to%20which%20periods%20are%20stigmatised%20in%20some%20tribal%20belts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%201985%2C%20when%20Dr%20Rani%20Bang%20(73)%2C%20an%20MD%20in%20obstetrics%20and%20gynaecology%20got%20wind%20of%20the%20death%20of%20an%2018-year-old%20who%20had%20succumbed%20to%20a%20snake%20bite%20while%20holed%20up%20in%20the%20kurma%20ghar%2C%20she%20was%20appalled.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20newly-married%20girl%20had%20been%20bitten%20by%20a%20cobra%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20found%20out.%20%E2%80%9CThough%20anti-venom%20was%20available%2C%20no%20one%20was%20ready%20to%20administer%20it%20to%20her%20while%20she%20was%20menstruating.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20snake%20bite%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20caused%20her%20death%3B%20a%20venomous%20ethos%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20Dr%20Rani%20unearthed%20the%20regressive%20interpretations%20of%20traditions%20that%20prevailed%20in%20Gadchiroli%2C%20the%20more%20aghast%20she%20was%20left.%20Ironically%2C%20antiquated%20concepts%20like%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekurma%20ghar%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewere%20revered.%20As%20she%20learnt%2C%20the%20edgy%20living%20setup%20could%20accommodate%20th