0The%20organisation%20runs%20a%2024%C3%977%20helpline%20and%20provides%20immediate%20support%20to%20survivors%20through%20its%2011%20one-stop%20centres%20established%20in%20each%20district%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20her%20advocacy%2C%20Prasanna%20aims%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F246382%2Fdelhi-mother-daughter-startup-fight-domestic-violence-empower-women-organic-spices-buy-online-home-business-india-gop94%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eempower%20survivors%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20educate%20the%20community%2C%20and%20work%20towards%20creating%20a%20society%20where%20violence%20is%20not%20tolerated%2C%20and%20all%20individuals%20are%20treated%20with%20dignity%20and%20respect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20suggests%20five%20ways%20to%20foster%20a%20culture%20of%20respect%2C%20equality%2C%20accountability%2C%20and%20a%20society%20that%20can%20work%20towards%20preventing%20domestic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-2-1728394782.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Prasanna%20runs%20a%2024x7%20helpline%20and%20provides%20immediate%20support%20to%20survivors%20through%20its%20one-stop%20centres.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-2-1728394782.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-2-1728394782-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-2-1728394782-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-2-1728394782-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%