20provide%20farmers%20with%20market%20linkages%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20drive%20through%20Hubbali%E2%80%99s%20beautiful%20landscapes%20makes%20one%20privy%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Emandis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(markets)%20and%20beautiful%20village%20homes%2C%20there%20are%20very%20few%20banks%20in%20sight.%20Pravesh%20explains%20the%20reason%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20parlance%20of%20the%20financial%20world%2C%20banks%20have%20not%20seen%20this%20sector%20as%20an%20attractive%20asset%20class.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20Samunnati%20enters.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20genius%20has%20been%20to%20show%20that%20this%20asset%20class%20can%20be%20a%20rewarding%20one%2C%20provided%20it%20is%20structured%20correctly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pravesh%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Samunnati%2C%20the%20focus%20is%20on%20smallholder%20farmers%20as%20the%20main%20beneficiaries%3B%20a%20paradigm%20shift%20in%20the%20existing%20economic%20view%20and%20opinions.%20But%20it%20was%20vital%20that%20the%20organisation%20be%20designed%20on%20this%20crux%20for%20Anil%2C%20whose%20two-decade-long%20association%20with%20the%20banking%20sector%20introduced%20him%20to%20the%20woes%20of%20agri-enterprises%20that%20lacked%20access%20to%20credit%20and%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20providing%20smallholder%20farmers%20and%20agri%20enterprises%20access%20to%20markets%2C%20financial%20intermediation%2C%20market%20linkages%20and%20advisory%20services%2C%20Samunnati%20enables%20them%20to%20operate%20at%20a%20higher%20equilibrium.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20is%20a%20standing%20example%20of%20how%20entrepreneurship%20can%20be%20targeted%20at%20providing%20commercially%20viable%20solutions%20to%20a%20customer%20segment%2C%20which%20is%20often%20misunderstood%2C%20and%20sidelined.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20operational%20results%20are%20a%20nod%20to%20their%20incredible%20work%2C%20Anil%20maintains%20that%20the%20organisation%20has%20a%20larger%20goal%20%E2%80%94%20to%20set%20an%20example.%20%E2%80%9CThrough%20Samunnati%2C%20we%20have%20established%20that%20lending%20to%20farmers%20is%20credible%2C%20sustainable%20and%20scalable.%20Samunnati%20has%20demonstrated%20the%20scalability%20of%20lending%20to%20agriculture%2C%20and%20this%20will%20foster%20a%20lot%20of%20banks%20coming%20into%20the%20sector.%20As%20I%20see%20it%2C%20the%20flow%20of%20credit%20to%20the%20agricultural%20sector%20is%20poised%20to%20take%20a%20big%20leap.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmer%20Mrutunjay%20Shankar%20Salimate%2C%20leader%20of%20Kalmeshwara%20FPO%2C%20which%20has%20benefitted%20from%20its%20association%20with%20Samunnati%2C%20reminisces%20how%20in%202016%20when%20they%20started%2C%20they%20were%20just%20a%20group%20of%2050%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20we%20have%20more%20than%201%2C400%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20The%20association%20with%20Samunnati%20has%20been%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20FPO%E2%80%99s%20work%20of%20supporting%20farmers%20with%20seeds%2C%20fertilisers%2C%20spray%20pumps%2C%20supply%20chain%20operations%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FAvbGO0-Rux8%3Fsi%3DaYFKg-1D4pcxdTAq%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrutunjay%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20provided%20us%20with%20market%20linkages%2C%20networking%20with%20institutions%20and%20financial%20support.%20They%20have%20also%20conducted%20activities%20to%20identify%20village-level%20entrepreneurs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarvaGram%20and%20Samunnati%E2%80%99s%20success%20stories%20are%20reflective%20of%20how%20entrepreneurs%20can%20create%20bus