n%20lies%20in%20heartwarming%20stories%20that%20Smita%20and%20Sumeet%20hear%20every%20now%20and%20then.%20Letting%20us%20in%20on%20one%20such%20anecdote%2C%20Smita%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20teacher%20who%20once%20took%20the%20LEAD%20tab%20in%20her%20hand%20and%20called%20it%20her%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eshikshan%20mitra%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(teacher%E2%80%99s%20friend).%20The%20reason%20for%20calling%20it%20this%2C%20the%20teacher%20went%20on%20to%20explain%2C%20was%20that%20the%20device%20guided%20her%2C%20taught%20her%20what%20to%20do%2C%20and%20gave%20her%20insights%20about%20her%20students.%20It%20was%20everything%20she%20needed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaking%20barriers%20and%20overcoming%20odds%20are%20central%20to%20these%20success%20stories%20you%E2%80%99ve%20just%20read.%20As%20the%20day%20wears%20on%2C%20a%20slight%20drizzle%20announces%20the%20arrival%20of%20dusk.%20Karnataka%20gears%20up%20for%20what%20promises%20to%20be%20a%20heavy%20downpour.%20Shops%20in%20the%20area%20down%20their%20shutters%2C%20and%20Ishwargowda%20Patil%20is%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-6-1727934739.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ishwargowda%20Basavanagowda%20Patil%20has%20a%20thriving%20field%20of%20green%20gram%20that%20he%20cultivates%20once%20he%20has%20wrapped%20up%20his%20kirana%20shop%20operations%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-6-1727934739.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-6-1727934739-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-6-1727934739-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-6-1727934739-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-6-1727934739-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368501%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIshwargowda%20Basavanagowda%20Patil%20has%20a%20thriving%20field%20of%20green%20gram%20that%20he%20cultivates%20once%20he%20has%20wrapped%20up%20his%20%3Cem%3Ekirana%3C%2Fem%3E%20shop%20operations%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20day%20isn%E2%80%99t%20over%20yet.%20He%20isn%E2%80%99t%20heading%20home%20yet%20%E2%80%93%20the%20vast%20fields%20of%20green%20gram%20await%20him.%20You%20see%2C%20Ishwargowda%20may%20be%20a%20businessman.%20But%2C%20he%20is%20essentially%20a%20farmer%20at%20heart.%20During%20a%20walk%20through%20his%20manicured%20fields%2C%20I%20observe%20how%20the%20land%20seems%20parched.%20But%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20drizzle%20has%20him%20relieved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20around%20the%20expanse%2C%20I%20notice%20how%20even%20in%20the%20most%20unfavourable%20conditions%2C%20green%20shoots%20have%20already%20pushed%20through%20the%20soil%20and%20emerged%20through%20the%20coarse%20rock%20%E2%80%94%20a%20story%20of%20resilience%2C%20I%20think%20to%20myself.%20While%20this%20is%20the%20story%20in%20the%20fields%2C%20a%20similar%20story%20of%20resilience%20is%20emerging%20across%20India%E2%80%99s%20towns%2C%20as%20entrepreneurs%20emerge%20into%20successful%20business%20owners%2C%20undaunted%20by%20the%20odds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20new%20face%20of%20India%3B%20one%20defined%20by%20aspirations%2C%20opportunities%2C%20dreams%2C%20and%20their%20realisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728370853000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22htt