iquid%20fertiliser.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Ftaruwar-3-1727440532.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Ftaruwar-3-1727440532-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Ftaruwar-3-1727440532-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Ftaruwar-3-1727440532-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Ftaruwar-3-1727440532-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367843%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20startup%20also%20converts%20leftover%20pulp%20from%20the%20fibre%20extraction%20into%20vermicompost%20and%20liquid%20fertiliser.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatyam%2C%20who%20looks%20after%20marketing%20and%20sales%20of%20the%20company%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20able%20to%20develop%20a%20good%20market%20base%20in%20India%20and%20now%20we%20aspire%20to%20enter%20into%20exports.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year%2C%20we%20will%20start%20exporting%20to%20other%20countries.%20A%20lot%20of%20companies%20are%20working%20on%20agriculture%20residues%20to%20make%20products%2C%20but%20our%20zero-waste%20approach%20helps%20us%20stand%20out%20in%20the%20market.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJagat%2C%20Satyam%2C%20and%20Nitish%20are%20not%20only%20entrepreneurs%20but%20also%20champions%20of%20sustainable%20innovation%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20a%20greener%20future%20and%20a%20more%20inclusive%20economy.%20Their%20initiative%20showcases%20the%20potential%20to%20create%20positive%20change%20by%20reimagining%20waste%20as%20a%20valuable%20resource%20and%20contributing%20to%20the%20circular%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20their%20dedication%20and%20vision%2C%20Taruwar%20demonstrates%20that%20small%20actions%20can