g%20to%20companies%2C%20we%20explain%20to%20them%20why%20it%20is%20important%20that%20they%20also%20give%20women%20an%20opportunity%20for%20the%20same%20role%20as%20they%20give%20men.%20Unlike%20days%20in%20the%20past%2C%20women%20today%20also%20travel%20and%20do%20night%20or%20second%20shifts%20while%20technology%20has%20upgraded%20and%20companies%20have%20the%20salary%20cap%20space.%20So%2C%20why%20not%20hire%20more%20capable%20women%20instead%20of%20leaving%20them%20out%3F%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20particularly%20unique%20about%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20that%20they%20are%20focused%20on%20delivering%20well-experienced%20talent%20for%20tech%20companies%20with%20a%20turnaround%20time%20of%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-1-1728052022.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20venture%20is%20looking%20to%20diversify%20the%20workplace%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-1-1728052022.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-1-1728052022-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-1-1728052022-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-1-1728052022-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-1-1728052022-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368856%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20Image%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20women%20to%20have%20more%20opportunities%20in%20tech%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pooja%20(Image%