3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20women%20really%20need%20is%20more%20help%20from%20their%20families%20like%20their%20husbands%2C%20in-laws%2C%20and%20relatives%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20household%20work.%20They%20must%20contribute%20a%20little%20more%20to%20unburden%20women%20from%20the%20responsibilities%20of%20household%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDespite%20the%20availability%20of%20daycare%20facilities%20in%20cities%2C%20there%20are%20families%20who%20do%20not%20like%20their%20children%20to%20be%20put%20up%20there.%20Of%20course%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20personal%20choice%20whether%20you%20want%20to%20put%20your%20child%20in%20a%20daycare%20facility%20or%20not%20but%20as%20times%20change%2C%20so%20should%20families.%20If%20families%20can%20support%20the%20idea%20of%20putting%20their%20children%20in%20a%20daycare%20facility%2C%20it%20would%20help%20working%20women%20a%20lot%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompanies%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20must%20do%20more%20to%20accommodate%20women%20by%20investing%20and%20setting%20up%20creches%20and%20day-care%20facilities%20for%20children%2C%20she%20argues.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20a%20recent%20visit%20to%20Sydney%2C%20I%20remember%20visiting%20a%20company%20that%20had%20a%20feeding%20room%20for%20new%20mothers%20and%20a%20creche%20facility%20overseen%20by%20a%20qualified%20caretaker%2C%20where%20children%20could%20play.%20Companies%20in%20India%20can%20afford%20to%20invest%20in%20such%20facilities%20and%20must%20progress%20with%20the%20times%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20SheWork.in%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fdiverse-office-portrait-talented-indian-girl-2078917600%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728099000000%2C%22v