ce-in-india-3-1726573323-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-3-1726573323-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366177%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%20boasts%2014%20rooms%20which%20can%20accommodate%20a%20total%20of%2040%20guests.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20delve%20further%20into%20history%2C%20Pallab%20draws%20attention%20to%20the%20notable%20parallels%20between%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%E2%80%99s%20functions%20and%20those%20of%20the%20palaces%20in%20England.%20%E2%80%9CAround%201924%2C%20the%20house%20had%20200%20guards.%20There%20was%20also%20the%20%E2%80%98Changing%20of%20the%20Guard%E2%80%99%20ceremony%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F48468%2Flieutenant-colonel-sophia-qureshi-indian-army%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emilitary%20drills%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20were%2034%20gardeners%2C%20innumerable%20staff%20and%20nine%20functioning%20kitchens.%E2%80%9D%20He%20laughs%20as%20he%20recounts%20the%20famous%20tea%20parties%20held%20at%20Cossimbazar%20Palace.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20crockery%20and%20cutlery%20for%20these%20were%20imported%20from%20England!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20in%201947%2C%20as%20India%20got%20freedom%2C%20and%20the%20estate%20system%20was%20abolished%20soon%20after%2C%20the%20fate%20of%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20took%20a%20drastic%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FVZaaCzClgxA%3Fsi%3D1WO9zmnnvPyi5MQ3%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20assets%20in%20our%20family%20were%20self-earned%20over%2010%20generations%3B%20they%20were%20not%20grants%20from%20the%20Government.%20But%20everything%20went%20away%20without%20a%20single%20%3Cem%3Epaisa%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Indian%20currency%20denomination)%3B%20they%20were%20auctioned.%20I%20have%20heard%20stories%20of%20how%20everything%20vanished%20overnight%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20laments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20grandfather%20would%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98From%20a%20king%2C%20I%20became%20a%20pauper%E2%80%99.%20The%20staff%20at%20the%20estate%2C%20the%20Government%2C%20and%20the%20system%20turned%20against%20him%20as%20dues%2C%20penalties%2C%20arrears%2C%20and%20international%20income%20issues%20began%20to%20surface.%20It%20was%20a%20miserable%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20solution%20that%20Raja%20Kamalaranjan%20Roy%20saw%20was%20to%20leave%20behind%20his%20Murshidabad%20house%20and%20shift%20to%20Kolkata%20with%20his%20family.%20It%20was%20here%20that%20Pallab%E2%80%99s%20parents%20married%20and%20a%20major%20part%20of%20his%20life%20would%20be%20spent%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333208%2Fwhere-to-eat-in-kolkata-classics-best-heritage-eateries-map-anindya-basu-dolon-dutta%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98City%20of%20Joy%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-4-1726573572.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22While%20the%20Roys%20pride%20themselves%20on%20their%20ancestral%20legacy%20that%20is%20now%20a%20heritage%20hotel%2C%20they%20also%20continue%20to%20lead%20their%20confectionery%20brand%20'Sugar%20and%20Spice'%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-4-1726573572.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-4-1726573572-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-4-1726573572-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-4-1726573572-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-4-1726573572-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366181%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhile%20the%20Roys%20pride%20themselves%20on%20their%20ancestral%20legacy%20that%20is%20now%20a%20heritage%20hotel%2C%20they%20also%20continue%20to%20lead%20their%20confectionery%20brand%20%E2%80%98Sugar%20and%20Spice%E2%80%99.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-5-1726573670.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20gives%20guests%20a%20peek%20into%20the%20colonial%20history%20of%20Murshidabad%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-5-1726573670.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-5-1726573670-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-5-1726573670-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-5-1726573670-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-5-1726573670-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366184%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20gives%20guests%20a%20peek%20into%20the%20colonial%20history%20of%20Murshidabad.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20was%20just%2013%20years%20old%20when%20she%20got%20married%20and%20I%20was%20born%20a%20year%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20shares%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20gets%20his%20resilience%20and%20optimism%20from%20her.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20had%20to%20forgo%20her%20education%20when%20I%20was%20born.%20But%20when%20I%20started%20school%2C%20she%20resumed%20studying.%20She%20graduated%2C%20got%20a%20national%20scholarship%20and%20qualified%20in%20hotel%20management.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20her%20new-found%20knowledge%20and%20culinary%20prowess%2C%20Supriya%20started%20a%20bakery%20in%20her%20house%20that%20in%20coming%20years%20would%20become%20a%20brand%2C%20%E2%80%98Sugar%20and%20Spice%E2%80%99.%20A%20common%20household%20name%20in%20the%20region%20today%2C%20%E2%80%98Sugar%20and%20Spice%E2%80%99%20has%20three%20factories%2C%20one%20each%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20Kasim%20Bazar%20and%20Siliguri.%20While%20the%20confectionery%20brand%20was%20one%20of%20the%20successful%20projects%20the%20family%20lays%20claim%20to%2C%20the%20other%20remains%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20grand%20%3Cem%3ERajbari%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERediscovering%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%3A%20From%20obscurity%20to%20opulence%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupriya%20Roy%E2%80%99s%20determination%20got%20the%20family%20brainstorming%20about%20ways%20in%20which%20they%20could%20revive%20the%20legacy%20of%20the%20ancestral%20palace.%20But%2060%20years%20of%20neglect%20meant%20that%20the%20palace%20had%20been%20made%20void%20of%20most%20of%20its%20treasures.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20furniture%2C%20aside%20from%20that%20in%20the%20main%20drawing%20room%2C%20had%20vanished.%20We%20are%20lucky%20to%20have%20some%20of%20the%20mirrors%2C%20sideboard%20tables%20and%20sofas%2C%20and%20have%20restored%20those.%20But%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F290529%2Fancient-photography-techniques-in-india-madhavan-pillai-research-india-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree%20generations%20of%20photos%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20lost%20when%20the%20house%20was%20cleaned%20by%20the%20Government%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20when%20they%20resolved%20to%20rebuild%20the%20ancestral%20property%20as%20a%20heritage%20hotel%2C%20attempts%20were%20made%20to%20retrieve%20these%20artefacts.%20Today%2C%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%2C%20boasting%2014%20rooms%2C%20which%20can%20accommodate%2040%20guests%20at%20a%20time%2C%20is%20a%20heritage%20hotel%20recognised%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Tourism%2C%20Government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20bear%20in%20mind%2C%20this%20recognition%20has%20come%20after%20decades%20of%20effort.%20Years%20ago%2C%20as%20the%20Roys%20vetted%20the%20situation%20that%20lay%20before%20them%20%E2%80%93%20a%20castle%20in%20ruins%20%E2%80%93%20they%20were%20perplexed%20about%20where%20to%20start.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20castle%20was%20a%20mediaeval%20one%20and%20so%20torches%20were%20popular.%20After%20the%20cleaning%20process%20was%20complete%2C%20we%20began%20work%20on%20the%20electricity%20and%20the%20wiring%2C%20the%20water%20connections%2C%20sinks%20and%20toilets.%20We%20had%20to%20replace%20broken%20furniture.%20And%20I%20think%20we%20changed%20almost%20500%20beams%20inside%20the%20palace%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-7-1726574151.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20colonial%20times%20the%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%20had%20proceedings%20similar%20to%20the%20Buckingham%20Palace%20of%20England%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-7-1726574151.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-7-1726574151-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-7-1726574151-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-7-1726574151-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-7-1726574151-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366186%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20colonial%20times%20the%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%20had%20proceedings%20similar%20to%20the%20Buckingham%20Palace%20of%20England.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20us%20on%20a%20virtual%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F365250%2Fvinyasa-earth-sankalp-sharma-sustainable-homestay-jaipur-artist-residencies-mud-bamboo-cob-lime%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etour%20of%20the%20magnificent%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20goes%20through%20a%20mental%20checklist%20of%20the%20sections%20of%20the%20palace%20that%20are%20completely%20restored%20%E2%80%94%20the%20front%20gates%2C%20the%20patio%2C%20the%20clock%20tower%2C%20the%20marble%20stairs%20leading%20into%20the%20main%20building%2C%20the%20north%20corridor%2C%20the%20ballroom%20annexes%2C%20dining%20room%20artefacts%2C%20Andar%20Mahal%20(an%20indoor%20space%20where%20the%20women%20of%20the%20palace%20lived)%2C%20some%20of%20the%20temples%20and%20the%20interior%20gardens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20was%20the%20legacy%20of%20the%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%20that%20it%20has%20been%20chronicled%20by%20books%20such%20as%20%E2%80%98A%20History%20of%20Murshidabad%E2%80%99%20by%20Major%20Walsh%20(1902)%20and%20%E2%80%98The%20Musnud%20of%20Murshidabad%E2%80%99%20(1905).%20They%20detail%20the%20fanfare%20and%20allure%20that%20Kasim%20Bazar%20enjoyed%20prior%20to%20the%20Battle%20of%20Plassey%20(1757)%20when%20the%20city%20was%20a%20major%20trading%20centre%20and%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20exporting%20hubs%20in%20the%20Eastern%20part%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20us%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20royal%20lineage%2C%20Pallab%20points%20to%20how%20the%20erstwhile%20British%20rulers%20used%20to%20create%20royalty%20by%20giving%20titles.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20were%20%3Cem%3Eraja%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Emaharaja%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Our%20family%20was%20recognised%20for%20our%20charitable%20work%20and%20three%20successive%20generations%20received%20the%20title%20of%20%3Cem%3Eraja%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%20Since%20this%20was%20an%20individual%20title%20it%20faded%20with%20the%20death%20of%20the%20person.%20This%20is%20why%2C%20Pallab%20explains%2C%20he%20and%20his%20father%20do%20not%20carry%20the%20title%20%3Cem%3Eraja%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPut%20your%20royal%20robes%20on!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20was%20the%20last%20time%20you%20were%20made%20to%20feel%20like%20royalty%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%2C%20mornings%20are%20both%20exciting%20and%20restful.%20Sip%20on%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%20(or%20many%20of%20them)%20as%20you%20relish%20your%20spread%20of%20breakfast.%20The%20stillness%20is%20broken%20only%20by%20the%20sound%20of%20birds.%20Whether%20it%20is%20a%2